data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath, 2 full car garage home. There are washer and dryer connections inside. Nice open floor plan. Eat in kitchen and breakfast bar. Large backyard, near schools & shopping. Carpets in the bedrooms. Vinyl flooring in Living, Hall, Kitchen, Entry, Dining, Laundry, Both Baths and Second Bedroom. This is an older home and has not been renovated or updated. The owner is unable to do so at this time. Nice yard for backyard bar b q's with back patio slab This home is a great investment property and fixxer upper. Come and get it. It wont last long.
